---

This project incorporates code from the SMDM project (Scaling up Masked
Diffusion Models on Text) by Nie et al., distributed under the MIT License.
The base model architectures (in src/mdm_unlearning/models/) and data loading
utilities (in src/mdm_unlearning/data/) are derived from SMDM.

SMDM repository: https://github.com/ML-GSAI/SMDM
SMDM paper: arXiv:2410.18514

The encoder-decoder masked diffusion architecture (enc_dec_diffmodel.py)
is inspired by E2D2 (Arriola et al., NeurIPS 2025).
E2D2 repository: https://github.com/kuleshov-group/e2d2
